OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fhomosexuality - Ghana      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fcardinal                   
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Homosexuality should not be a criminal 
OL,6, offence and people should be helped to 
OL,7, understand the issue better, a top     
OL,8, cardinal from Ghana has told the BBC.  
OL,10,FCardinal Peter Turkson's comments come 
OL,11,Fas parliament discusses a bill imposing
OL,12,Fharsh penalties on LGBT people.        
OL,14,FHis views are at odds with Roman       
OL,15,FCatholic bishops in Ghana, who say     
OL,16,Fhomosexuality is "despicable".         
OL,18,FLast month, Pope Francis suggested he  
OL,19,Fwould be open to having the Catholic   
OL,20,FChurch bless same-sex couples.         
